'''Scorpions''' are [[aggressive]] [[monster]]s. They are often considered annoying to players training mining in certain locations.

==Locations==
*[[Al-Kharid mine]]
*[[Dwarven Mines]] (regular and king scorpions)
*[[Karamja Volcano]] area (regular scorpions only)
*[[Kharazi Jungle]] dungeon inside [[Strange Barrel]]s.
*[[Temple of Ikov]] under the bridge where [[Boots of lightfootedness]] are needed

